{"schemaVersion":2,"book":"PHM","name":"Filemón","chapters":{"1":{"1":{"text":"Pablo, prisionero de Cristo Jesús, y el hermano Timoteo: ¶ A Filemón nuestro amado hermano y colaborador,","segments":[{"text":"Pablo","morph":"NNSM","strong":"G3972"},{"text":", prisionero","morph":"NNSM","strong":"G1198"},{"text":"de Cristo","morph":"NGSM","strong":"G5547"},{"text":"Jesús","morph":"NGSM","strong":"G2424"},{"text":", y","morph":"CLN","strong":"G2532"},{"text":"el","morph":"DNSM","strong":"G3588"},{"text":"hermano","morph":"NNSM","strong":"G80"},{"text":"Timoteo","morph":"NNSM","strong":"G5095"},{"text":": ¶ A Filemón","morph":"NDSM","strong":"G5371"},{"text":"nuestro","morph":"RP1GP","strong":"G2257"},{"text":"amado","morph":"DDSM"},{"text":"hermano y","morph":"CLN","strong":"G2532"},{"text":"colaborador","morph":"JDSM","strong":"G4904"},{"text":","}]},"2":{"text":"y a la hermana Apia, y a Arquipo, nuestro compañero de milicia, y a la iglesia que está en tu casa:","segments":[{"text":"y","morph":"CLN","strong":"G2532"},{"text":"a la","morph":"DDSF","strong":"G3588"},{"text":"hermana","morph":"NDSF","strong":"G79"},{"text":"Apia","morph":"NDSF","strong":"G682"},{"text":", y","morph":"CLN","strong":"G2532"},{"text":"a Arquipo","morph":"NDSM","strong":"G751"},{"text":", nuestro","morph":"RP1GP","strong":"G2257"},{"text":"compañero","morph":"DDSM"},{"text":"de milicia, y","morph":"CLN","strong":"G2532"},{"text":"a la","morph":"DDSF","strong":"G3588"},{"text":"iglesia","morph":"NDSF","strong":"G1577"},{"text":"que","morph":"P","strong":"G2596"},{"text":"está en tu","morph":"RP2GS","strong":"G4675"},{"text":"casa","morph":"NASM","strong":"G3624"},{"text":":"}]},"3":{"text":"Gracia a vosotros y paz de Dios nuestro Padre y del Señor Jesucristo.","segments":[{"text":"Gracia","morph":"NNSF","strong":"G5485"},{"text":"a vosotros","morph":"RP2DP","strong":"G5213"},{"text":"y","morph":"CLN","strong":"G2532"},{"text":"paz","morph":"NNSF","strong":"G1515"},{"text":"de","morph":"P","str